{
  "stem": "5758.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I want you to go to a place, which is in the occupied zone near Macon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I went to see that fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I told him again the truth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he introduced me up the hill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was down the Montagnes Saint-Cyr, near Macon, which-- and I found a lot of young people there, people who didn't want to work in Germany because-- I don't know whether you realize, the young people had to go-- if the Germans wanted to-- had to go and work in Germany as, as workers, laborers.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And a lot of young people didn't want to work in Germany, a lot of communists and socialists, and quite a few Jews there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were hiding up in the, [INAUDIBLE], in the mountain, in caves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were organizing food from peasants who had-- were surrounding us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Sometimes we had to steal food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Sometimes we had to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whatever money we had, you know, go and get-- buy some food in, in villages.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] this-- in 1942, I believe, I joined.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In 1942, I joined the resistance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Just a second.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Actually, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was in-- somewhere in summer, in summer, 19-- beginning, 1943, actually.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we didn't do very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Once, we blew up a, a, a, a train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Or we tried to blew up a train with, with German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I do not know really what the result was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because as soon as we placed the explosions on the, on the rail and the train was coming, we all run away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But we understand later on that the train derailed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But apart from injuries, we didn't, unfortunately, kill any soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This was the only thing that really I remember vividly.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
